assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: TCI Developers Limited engages in the real estate and warehousing development businesses in India. The company rents or leases land, office complexes, residential buildings, warehouses, and logistics parks. It also provides project management services for construction projects. The company was founded in 2008 and is based in Gurugram, India.
